# Test before push

Do not push to the remote until the full applicable test suite passes:

- Unit tests (`tests/unit/`)
- Integration tests (`tests/integration/`)
- E2E/UI tests (`tests/e2e/`) when the app has a UI

Document exceptions in the journal if tests cannot pass. Use **git-workflow** only after tests are green (or exceptions are recorded).
